  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Coordinating and overseeing all aspects of projects</li><li>Manage project documentation and tracking.</li><li>Facilitate design, production, and delivery processes.</li><li>Coordinating with various stakeholders, including clients, subcontractors and suppliers, to ensure timely delivery of projects</li><li>Support the Project Management Team in project implementation</li><li>Coordinate daily manpower allocation, ensure work activities are conducted properly, in accordance to construction / shop drawings</li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Architectural / Construction / Civil Engineering or a related technical field</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in a project engineering or project coordination role.</li><li>Strong technical knowledge and problem-solving skills, with the ability to interpret engineering drawings and data</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams</li><li>Familiarity with relevant industry standards, regulations, and safety practices</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; </strong></a><strong>ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p>",
